	<div style="text-align:right;">
		DAMASIO, Ricardo Augusto<sup>1</sup>; FREITAS, Kamyla Thais Dias de<sup>2</sup>; SILVA, Walan Robert da<sup>3</sup>; LISBOA, Tailine<sup>4</sup>; BRAGA, Rafael Kanitz<sup>5</sup>		<BR>
